&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Model complex structured finance transactions:&lt;/strong&gt; You will extract deal structures from offering memorandums, trustee reports, and other legal documents and create programmatic representations of the deals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Enhance and go to market with dv01’s revolutionary on-demand reporting tool: &lt;/strong&gt;Partner internally with Credit Facility Reporting team to further develop the client-facing on-demand borrowing base reporting tool.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
